              <Font Type="MyObjectBuilder_FontDefinition" Subtype="Red" />
              <FontSize>1.261</FontSize>
              <PublicDescription>KEEEEEEEEEEN

Please fix those timer blocks
so we can again build nice 
torpedo launchers. Or at least 
give us some vanilla primary
weapon, a rail gun or a torpedo 
bay, a nuke launcher, I dont care. 

Sincerely, JD &lt;3</PublicDescription>
